┐Jan Mathews
The key was turned, the gates were opened wide
St Peter and woman walked inside and there
within the sunshine of the throne,
She saw the little Garden she had grown
1939-2010"─
┴Here is where good friends should meet
To laugh and talk on Sammy's seat
In loving memory of
Samantha Jane Thompson 1981 - 2009
She brought laughter into our lives
and love into our hearts"┘
ųWE LOVED IT HERE YOU LOVED IT HERE.
YOUR DOG KASHKA LOVED IT HERE.
I LOVE YOU STILL AND ALWAYS WILL
TO MY DARLING STUART PANTREY
BORN 3/1/65 - DIED 20/9/10
GRIEF IS THE PRICE WE PAY FOR LOVE
RICHARD FAIRBRASS"▄
